title: Chipotle
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fast food chain where you could customize your order (tacos, burritos, mexican bowls) and request no cheese/dairy. As of July 2014, vegan tofu based sofritas filling is not yet served in Michigan locations; however, according to their website, they plan to expand soon.
